## File->Preference->Setting
```json
// Place your settings in this file to overwrite the default settings
{
  "editor.tabSize": 4,
  "editor.rulers": [
    145
  ],
  "editor.fontFamily": "Yahei monaco",
  "editor.fontSize": 16,
  "editor.wordWrap": "on"
}
```

## extension tools
cpp-tools
c++ intellisense
c/c++ clang command adapter
c/cpp snippets